news.title: Pune: EOW registers Rs 9 crore cheating case on Nirman Corporation's directors
news.para: In April 2016, he invested Rs9.11 crore in 15 flats at the scheme Nirmann Serrene in Undri and a shop in the other scheme, Estrella, both developed by the Nirman Corporation and its associate firm.

news.title: Goa: Building nod to be deemed if panchayat, BDO don't act in 60 days
news.para: If a person applies for a construction licence and the panchayat and block development officer (BDO) do not take any decision within 60 days, then the permission will be deemed granted.

news.title: Faulty land records derail patta transfer in Tamil Nadu: CAG
news.para: The report has lauded the state government for increase in digitization of land records, leading to improvisation of access and transparency.
